## Proposed Changes

### Navigation & Layout

#### [MODIFY] [NavMenu.razor](file:///c:/Users/Admin/source/Workspaces/2026/Vns-Epr-Blazor-2026/Vns-Epr-Blazor-2026/Vns-Epr-Blazor-2026/Components/Layout/NavMenu.razor)

Replace the static main `<DxMenu>` block with role-aware menu items:

| Menu Item | Visibility | Icon |
|---|---|---|
| Home | All authenticated users | `icon-home` |
| Dashboard | All authenticated users | `icon-counter` *(reuse existing)* |
| User Management | `SuperAdmin, Admin` only | `icon-settings` |
| System Settings | `SuperAdmin` only | `icon-settings` |

**Implementation approach:** Wrap restricted items using `<AuthorizeView Roles="...">`. Since `<DxMenu>` → `<Items>` only accepts `<DxMenuItem>`, we cannot nest `<AuthorizeView>` directly inside `<Items>`. Instead, we will use **two separate `<DxMenu>`** blocks:
1. A menu for items visible to all authenticated users (Home, Dashboard).
2. A menu wrapped in `<AuthorizeView Roles="SuperAdmin, Admin">` for admin-only items (User Management, System Settings), with the `SuperAdmin`-only item nested using a second `<AuthorizeView>`.

